SHIGEMA AOKI, Appellant, v. Edward L. HAFF, District Director of Immigration, Port of San Francisco, Appellee. No. 7573. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 15, 1935. Stephen M. White, of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. IT. H. McPike and Robert L. McWilliams, Asst. U. S. Attys., both of San Francisco (Arthur J. Phelan, U. S. Immigration and Naturalization Service, of San Francisco, Cal., on the brief), for appellee.

Before GARRECHT, DENMAN, and MATHEWS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed ; mandate forthwith.
